In self_improve.py and meta-layer updates:

- Log EVERY meta-graph change (old rule → new rule, reason, before/after metrics).
- Run at least one small test loop after update to measure efficiency / success rate change.
- Only accept improvements that show ≥5% better hypothesis acceptance or loop speed.